%% ModelMesh Serving - Component Structure Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Controller"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Go Operator]
        SRReconciler[ServingRuntime<br/>Reconciler]
        PReconciler[Predictor<br/>Reconciler]
        SvcReconciler[Service<br/>Reconciler]
        AutoReconciler[Autoscaler<br/>Reconciler]
        Webhook[ServingRuntime<br/>Webhook<br/>9443/TCP]

        Controller --> SRReconciler
        Controller --> PReconciler
        Controller --> SvcReconciler
        Controller --> AutoReconciler
        Controller --> Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pod (per ServingRuntime)"
        MM[ModelMesh Container<br/>Java - LiteLinks<br/>8033/TCP gRPC]
        OAuthProxy[oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        RESTProxy[rest-proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP]
        Puller[Storage Helper/Puller<br/>Model Download]
        Adapter[Built-in Adapter<br/>triton/mlserver/ovms]
        ModelServer[Model Server Container<br/>User-specified]

        OAuthProxy -->|forwards to| RESTProxy
        RESTProxy -->|gRPC| MM
        MM -->|inference| ModelServer
        MM -->|model ops| Adapter
        Puller -->|model artifacts| ModelServer
    end

    %% CRDs
    User[User / Data Scientist] -->|creates| SRCR[ServingRuntime CR]
    User -->|creates| CSRCR[ClusterServingRuntime CR]
    User -->|creates| PredictorCR[Predictor CR]
    User -->|creates| ISCR[InferenceService CR]

    SRCR -->|watched by| SRReconciler
    CSRCR -->|watched by| SRReconciler
    PredictorCR -->|watched by| PReconciler
    ISCR -->|watched by| PReconciler

    SRReconciler -->|creates/manages| RuntimePod[Runtime Deployment]
    PReconciler -->|VModel API| MM
    SvcReconciler -->|creates| InferenceService[Inference Service<br/>ClusterIP]
    AutoReconciler -->|manages| HPA[HorizontalPodAutoscaler]

    %% External Dependencies
    Controller -->|watches/updates| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP]
    MM -->|coordination| etcd[etcd<br/>2379/TCP]
    Puller -->|downloads models| S3[Object Storage<br/>S3/MinIO<br/>443/TCP]
    OAuthProxy -->|validates tokens| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
    SvcReconciler -->|creates| ServiceMonitor[ServiceMonitor<br/>Prometheus]

